---
// Three floating glass-morphism chips around the phone mockup.
// Honesty contracts applied: "Bodycam Live · Recording" replaced with
// "Photo documentation · Every job" (the bodycam pilot is Q4 2026).
---

<div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 hidden md:block" aria-hidden="true">
  <div
    class="absolute left-[6%] top-[18%] flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-line-darker bg-white/8 px-4 py-2 font-mono text-xs font-medium text-bone shadow-lg backdrop-blur-md"
  >
    <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-success animate-live-pulse"></span>
    Verified &middot; BC registered
  </div>

  <div
    class="absolute right-[4%] top-[32%] flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-line-darker bg-white/8 px-4 py-2 font-mono text-xs font-medium text-bone shadow-lg backdrop-blur-md"
  >
    <span class="text-teal-glow">●</span>
    AI inventory <span class="text-mist-dim">&middot; Q3 2026</span>
  </div>

  <div
    class="absolute left-[8%] bottom-[20%] flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-line-darker bg-white/8 px-4 py-2 font-mono text-xs font-medium text-bone shadow-lg backdrop-blur-md"
  >
    <span class="text-ember-warm">◉</span>
    Photo documentation &middot; Every job
  </div>
</div>
